Capt. Khanysile Zwane, Middelburg police spokesperson, said police were called to the scene on Saturday night just after 19:00. According to information from bystanders, a pregnant woman was shot in the stomach whilst cooking dinner for her husband. Two men were arrested in connection with the incident and the gun that was suspected to be involved was recovered next to the N4 where it was dumped. The men are expected to appear in the Middelburg Magistrateâ€™s Court today.